text: Tatyana Nikolayevna Khromova (Татьяна Николаевна Хромова; born ) was an Uzbekistani born Kazakhstani female weightlifter, competing in the 75 kg category and representing Kazakhstan at international competitions. She participated at the 2000 Summer Olympics in the 75 kg event, and at the 2004 Summer Olympics in the 75 kg event.
